quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  87,1,Apney buhat hi buland Allah kay nam ki pakizgi biyan ker
  87,2,Jissney paida kiya aur sahi salim banaya
  87,3,Aur jiss na(thek thak)andaza kiya aur phir rah dekhai
  87,4,Aur jis nay taza ghass paida ki
  87,5,Phir ussney is ko (sukha ker )siyah kora ker diya
  87,6,Hum tujhy parhaein gay phir tu na bhoolay ga
  87,7,Magar jo kuch Allah chahey wo zahir aur poshida ko janta hay
  87,8,Hum apky liey asani paida kerdein gay
  87,9,To ap nasehat kerty rahein ager nasehat kuch faida dy
  87,10,Derney wala to nasehat lyga
  87,11,(han)badbakht is say gurez karey ga
  87,12,Jo bari aag mein jaey ga
  87,13,Jahan phir won a mary ga jnajeiy ga(balky halat e nazah mein para rahy ga)
  87,14,Besahk usney falah pali jo pak hogaya
  87,15,Aur jis nay apney rab ka nam yad rakha aur namaz parhta raha
  87,16,Lakin tum to duniya ki zindagi ko tarjeeh dyty ho
  87,17,Aur akhrat buhat bhyter aur baqa wali hay
  87,18,Yeh batein phyli kitabon mein bhi hein
  87,19,(yani) Ibrahim aur Musa ki kitabon mein